Roles
=====

Simple roles system.

Migrations
=====

  create_table :roles do |t|
    t.string :name
  end
  Role.create(:name => "administrator")


  create_table :privileges, :id => false do |t|
    t.integer :user_id
    t.integer :role_id
  end


